channel.title: New keyboard/mouse + power supply
channel.description:
I would like to buy a new keyboard and mouse because the ones I use now are almost broken. It would be nice if they were back and white, glossy to fit with my case (inb4 gay) and wireless. Under 100$ would be nice too.
Anyone got an idea?
Also my power supply started to do some pretty strange noise (I think it's the fan's bearing), and from what I read I can't fix that. So would anyone know one (under 150$) that could handle my comp and maybe a better GPU too? Here are my specs:
Asus P5B-Plus "Green" 3GB RAM Kingston nVidia 8500GT "Forsa" Intel Core2Duo E4440 2.0GHz 80GB Seagate HDD 250GB Maxtor HDD
Thanks!
